<p id="coin-slider"><img src="/images/safety/slider/AQ_health-w600-346.png" style="width: 600px; height: 346px;" /> <img src="/images/safety/slider/airquality_alertsWd600x346.png" style="width: 600px; height: 346px;" /> <img src="/images/safety/slider/AQ-pollutants600x346img.png" style="width: 600px; height: 346px;" /></p>
